    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ガイ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Guy</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>さぁ食べろ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Now eat it!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>身体にもいいから、食べなさい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's good for you, so eat it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うぷっ……。
あーまじぃ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Augh...
Agh... Gross.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>16</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>よし、ちゃんと食べたな。
よかった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Alright, be sure to eat it properly.
I'm happy for you.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>おたくら、いったい何者なんだ？
本当にわざわざ
食べ残しをさせない為に来たのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Who the heck are you nerds?
Did you really come all the way
here for the sake of food waste?</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Guy uses おたくら here, so I used nerds for that.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>17</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そうよ。
アスベルが食べ物を守るって聞かなくて</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's right. Asbel wouldn't hear it
once it came to protecting the food.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>それは大変だったろうな、あんたも</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That must've been pretty crazy for you, too.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>17</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ええ、とても大変。
あなたも苦労してそうね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes, it was very crazy.
You also look to be having troubles of your own.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>29</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんの話だ、シェリア？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What are you talking about, Cheria?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>28</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
